Info about blockchainJs (install & more.. )


#ts-node allows to read typescript files without compilation , nodemon restarts nodejs automatically
npm install --save-dev ts-node nodemon

------------------
nodemon.json file:
------------------
{
  "watch": ["src"], // Location to watch by nodemon 
  "ext": "ts",
  "exec": "ts-node ./src/index.ts"
}




#To start dev node :
npm run dev

